&lt;BCI Holdings Corp>  said its &lt;BeatriceU.S. Food Corp> retained Shearson Lehman Brothers Inc to assistin the sale of its national bottled water business.    It said products of the subsidiary, based in Monterey Park,Calif., are sold under the Arrowhead brand name in Californiaand Arizona, the Ozarka name in Texas and the Great Bear namein 11 northeastern states. Reuter&#3;